{"tid":1306734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大：近一成人過去兩周現抑鬱徵狀　部分人曾萌自殺念頭","createTime":"2019-07-11T09:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T09:16:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"380747de8e8fdc16cc8f6f77aa841f5a75c1be4b","tid":1306734,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港大學公共衞生學院研究顯示，過去兩周有近一成受訪者出現抑鬱症徵狀，部分人曾有自殺念頭。<br />\n<br />\n港大上月22日至本月7日，以電話訪問1200多名成年人，發現9.1%受訪者出現抑鬱徵狀，高於2014年佔中期間的5.3%，當中有4.6%受訪者曾出現自殺念頭，同樣高於佔中期間的3.6%。<br />\n<br />\n港大數據顯示，不論受訪者有沒有參與遊行或示威衝突，還是原本支持逃犯條例修訂，都有抑鬱徵狀，而且在年長群組較為顯著。港大公共衞生學院分析認為，重大社會事件影響整體市民的精神狀況，呼籲大眾關心自己和身邊人。"},{"pid":"ff7ea0a8988ca9964fbc565c4db23487058a2f35","tid":1306734,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:16:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=355037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355037&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=9f30a8e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355037&h=5c696440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=355037</a>"}]}